extendedInfo.description: Insta Money - Multi Bank Mobile Banking application.The application helps you generate Mobile Money Identifier (MMID) for your bank accounts and send money to anyone with IMPS enabled bank account across india. Read more about IMPS here http://www.npci.org.in/aboutimps.aspx.You can also check your bank balance, get a mini statement and recharge your mobile.Following Banks are supported:Allahabad BankAndhra BankAxis BankBank Of IndiaBank of MaharashtraCanara BankCiti BankCity Union BankCorporation BankDena BankDevelopment Credit BankDhanalakshmi BankDombivli Nagari Sahakari BankFederal BankHDFC BankHSBC BankICICI BankIDBI BankING Vysya BankIndian BankIndian Overseas BankIndus Ind BankJammu & Kashmir BankKarnataka BankKarur Vysya BankKotak MahindraLakshmi Vilas BankOriental Bank of CommercePunjab & Sind BankPunjab National BankRatnakar BankSouth Indian BankStandard Chartered BankState Bank Of Bikaner & JaipurState Bank Of HyderabadState Bank Of IndiaState Bank Of TravancoreState Bank of PatialaState Bank of TravancoreSyndicate BankTamilnadu Mercantile BankUnion Bank Of IndiaUnited Bank Of IndiaVijaya BankYes Bank

reviews.title: Useful app
reviews.comment: Not many are aware of the Interbank Mobile Payment Service (IMPS) that most banks in India supports. It facilitates people to send money instantly to any bank accounts in India using their mobile phone.  Useful app for quick money transfer to dear and near ones.
